CellSample.protocol:
Thaw in recovery media: 1:1 RPMI:FBS 24 hours then split into RPMI-1640 15% FBS.
Culture in media depth of .2ml/cm2 splitting by dilution until volume reaches 100 mL.
Transfer to erlenmeyer style 500 mL shaker flask with 200 mL volume shaking at 90 rpm.
Freeze in RPMI-1640 15% FBS with final volume 10% DMSO.

Culture in RPMI-1640 10% FBS. Split by rinsing with PBS and trypsininzing with 0.05% trypsin-EDTA.
Freeze in RPMI-1640 10% FBS with final volume 10% DMSO.

Culture in RPMI-1640 10% FBS. Split by rinsing with PBS and trypsininzing with 0.05% trypsin-EDTA.
Freeze in RPMI-1640 10% FBS with final volume 10% DMSO.
